# Dashboards

## housing_market_analytics.pbix

This Power BI dashboard was built using the Boston Housing dataset
as part of the Level 3 Advanced task for the Codveda Technologies
Data Analysis Internship.

### Dashboard Contents

**KPI Cards**
Average Home Value, Average Rooms, Average Crime Rate, High Value Homes

**Visualisations**
- Scatter chart: Rooms vs Home Value by Price Tier
- Bar chart: Average Home Value by Accessibility Index
- Line chart: Lower Status Percentage vs Home Value
- Treemap: Distribution by Price Tier
- Column chart: Crime Rate by Price Tier

**Slicers**
- Price Tier (High, Mid, Low)
- River Adjacent (Yes, No)
- Crime Rate range slider

### Tools Used
Microsoft Power BI Desktop

DAX (calculated measures and columns)

Power Query (data transformation)

